'''愛丁堡國際電影節'''（{{lang-en|Edinburgh International Film Festival}}）是一個於每年六月在[[英國|英國]][[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]舉辦的電影節。

==历史==
愛丁堡國際電影節於1947年開始舉辦，2007年之前在每年八月舉行，是世界歷史最古老的電影節之一<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.scotland.com/blog/scotland-hosts-the-worlds-longest-running-film-festival | title = Scotland Hosts the World's Longest Running Film Festival | work = Scotland.com | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | archive-date = 2018-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180713200848/http://www.scotland.com/blog/scotland-hosts-the-worlds-longest-running-film-festival | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.webfilmfest.com/ | title = WebFilmFest.com - Your Online Source for Film Festivals | work = WebFilmFest.com | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | archive-date = 2016-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161009090758/http://webfilmfest.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://travelguides.lastminute.com/sisp/index.htm?fx=event&event_id=12069 | title = Filmhouse - Edinburgh International Film Festival | work = lastminute.com | accessdate = 2010-04-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100412004151/http://travelguides.lastminute.com/sisp/index.htm?fx=event&event_id=12069 | archive-date = 2010-04-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。創建之初愛丁堡國際電影節主要展示紀錄片類作品，但現在則網羅各種領域。
